1082void DeathKnightUnderstudyAI::Destroy()
1083{
1084 if (mRazuviousAI != NULL)
1085 {
1086 std::set< DeathKnightUnderstudyAI* >::iterator Iter = mRazuviousAI->mStudents.find(this);
1087 if (Iter != mRazuviousAI->mStudents.end())
1088 mRazuviousAI->mStudents.erase(Iter);
1089
1090 mRazuviousAI = NULL;
1091 };
1092
1093 delete this;
1094};

2650 void AIUpdate() override
2651 {
2652 switch (m_phase)
2653 {
2654 case 1:
2655 PhaseOne();
2656 break;
2657 case 2:
2658 PhaseTwo();
2659 break;
2660 case 3:
2661 PhaseThree();
2662 break;
2663 default:
2664 {
2665 }
2666 }
2667 }
2668
2669 void PhaseOne()
2670 {
2671 if (EventStart == true)
2672 {
2673 SpawnTimer++;
2674 if (SpawnTimer == 5 || SpawnTimer == 10)
2675 {
2676 for (uint8_t i = 0; i < 7; i++)
2677 {
2678 int Counter = 0;
2679
2680 while (Counter == 0)
2681 {
2682 if (FrozenWastes[i] == false && (Util::getRandomUInt(3) == 0 || SpawnCounter > 0))
2683 {
2684 for (uint8_t x = 0; x < 10; x++)
2685 {
2686 uint32_t SpawnID = 10 * i + x;
2687 spawnCreature(CN_SOLDIER_OF_THE_FROZEN_WASTES, SFrozenWastes[SpawnID].x, SFrozenWastes[SpawnID].y, SFrozenWastes[SpawnID].z, SFrozenWastes[SpawnID].o);
2688 }
2689
2690 FrozenWastes[i] = true;
2691 Counter++;
2692 }
2693
2694 if (Abominations[i] == false && (Util::getRandomUInt(3) == 0 || SpawnCounter > 0))
2695 {
2696 for (uint8_t x = 0; x < 3; x++)
2697 {
2698 uint32_t SpawnID = 3 * i + x;
2699 spawnCreature(CN_UNSTOPPABLE_ABOMINATION, Abomination[SpawnID].x, Abomination[SpawnID].y, Abomination[SpawnID].z, Abomination[SpawnID].o);
2700 }
2701
2702 Abominations[i] = true;
2703 Counter++;
2704 }
2705
2706 if (SoulWeavers[i] == false && ((Util::getRandomUInt(3) == 0 && Counter < 2) || Counter == 0 || SpawnCounter > 0))
2707 {
2708 uint32_t SpawnID = i;
2709 spawnCreature(CN_SOUL_WEAVER, SoulWeaver[SpawnID].x, SoulWeaver[SpawnID].y, SoulWeaver[SpawnID].z, SoulWeaver[SpawnID].o);
2710
2711 SoulWeavers[i] = true;
2712 Counter++;
2713 }
2714
2715 if (SoulWeavers[i] == true && Abominations[i] == true && FrozenWastes[i] == true)
2716 Counter = 1;
2717 }
2718 }
2719
2720 SpawnCounter++;
2721 }
2722
2723 if (SpawnCounter == 2)
2724 {
2725 for (uint8_t i = 0; i < 7; i++)
2726 {
2727 FrozenWastes[i] = false;
2728 Abominations[i] = false;
2729 SoulWeavers[i] = false;
2730 }
2731
2732 WaveTimer = Util::getRandomUInt(10, 16);
2733 EventStart = false;
2734 SpawnCounter = 0;
2735 PhaseTimer = 310;
2736 SpawnTimer = 0;
2737 }
2738 }
2739
2740 else
2741 {
2742 PhaseTimer--;
2743 WaveTimer--;
2744
2745 if (PhaseTimer == 5)
2746 {
2747 switch (Util::getRandomUInt(2))
2748 {
2749 case 0:
2750 getCreature()->sendChatMessage(CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_YELL, LANG_UNIVERSAL, "Pray for mercy!");
2751 getCreature()->PlaySoundToSet(8809);
2752 break;
2753 case 1:
2754 getCreature()->sendChatMessage(CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_YELL, LANG_UNIVERSAL, "Scream your dying breath!");
2755 getCreature()->PlaySoundToSet(8810);
2756 break;
2757 case 2:
2758 getCreature()->sendChatMessage(CHAT_MSG_MONSTER_YELL, LANG_UNIVERSAL, "The end is upon you!");
2759 getCreature()->PlaySoundToSet(8811);
2760 break;
2761 }
2762 }
2763
2764 if (PhaseTimer == 3)
2765 DespawnTrash = true;
2766
2767 if (!PhaseTimer)
2768 {
2769 getCreature()->setChannelObjectGuid(0);
2770 getCreature()->setChannelSpellId(0);
2771 _setMeleeDisabled(false);
2772 getCreature()->removeUnitFlags(UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
2773 getCreature()->setControlled(false, UNIT_STATE_ROOTED);
2774
2775 DespawnTrash = false;
2776 HelpDialog = 0;
2777 GCounter = 0;
